le meilleure album du groupe c'est incontestablement leur meilleur album , trop souvent eclipsé par le neanmois grand `` dark side of the moon '' de 1973 ... syd barrett ( chanteur , guitariste ) est un génie probablement trop fragile pour ce monde opressant ... mais il nous a laissé se temoignage de sa vision ... il avait comme acces musicalement à tous ses reves ... l'album en lui meme sonne comme un reverie eveillée ... et il y en a peu qui delivre une telle orfevrerie de psychedelisme aussi divers ... de l'extraterrestre `` astronomy domine '' à la petite comptine typiquement anglaise `` bike '' ( me faisant penser aux premiers blur ) ... ils changent de style mais la magie est là ... et `` scarecrow '' ou `` chapter 24 '' sont parmis les meilleurs titres de pop psychedelique ayant heurté terre ... ||| the best album of the group is undoubtedly their best album , too often eclipsed by the great neanmois `` dark side of the moon '' in 1973 ... syd barrett ( vocals , guitar ) is a genius probably too fragile for this world oppression ... but he left us is testimony to his vision ... it was as musically accessible to all his dreams ... the album in him even sounds like a waking dream ... and there are few who issues such a goldsmiths of psychedelic ... ranging from the extraterrestrial `` astronomy domine '' the little rhyme typical english `` bike '' ( making me think of the first blur ) ... they change their style but the magic is here ... and `` scarecrow '' or `` chapter 24 '' are among the best tracks of psychedelic pop that struck earth ...